how to create map
=================

start in terminal:
	robot-mapping.sh
and then start in other terminal:
	bag-record.sh
and then start in other terminal:
	rviz.sh

joystick robot around (be slow, especially turn slowly)

when the mapping is finished, run in other terminal:
	map-snapshot.sh

it should end automatically
then kill:
	bag-record.sh
then kill:
	rviz.sh
	robot-mapping.sh


how to re-create map
====================

start in terminal:
	bag-mapping.sh
and then start in other terminal:
	rviz.sh
and then start in other terminal:
	bag-play.sh
will list all bags
	bag-play.sh [bagname]
	map-snapshot.sh
